    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>《Ground Zero》是一款复古生存恐怖游戏，故事设定在末日后的韩国。</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场陨石浩劫几乎摧毁了整个国家。两个月后，尘埃落定、雷暴消散，空气不再致命。一名韩国精英特工与她的加拿大搭档被派往灾区展开调查。而在迷雾笼罩的废墟中等待他们的，是远超他们想象的可怕存在...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/fad486f1957cdb5dcbe145081381c7fc.poster.avif?t=1762784991\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/fad486f1957cdb5dcbe145081381c7fc.webm?t=1762784991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/fad486f1957cdb5dcbe145081381c7fc.mp4?t=1762784991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与潜伏在釜山阴暗角落中的怪物交战，它们因陨石撞击后的辐射沉降而发生异变。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/ab26598c5f4f6f3f329643614180e439.poster.avif?t=1762784991\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/ab26598c5f4f6f3f329643614180e439.webm?t=1762784991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/ab26598c5f4f6f3f329643614180e439.mp4?t=1762784991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >查明当日撞击釜山的究竟是什么。那些自撞击后不断蔓延的诡异生长物到什么，又为何会腐蚀灾后仅存的生命？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索这座陷入废墟的美丽城市，从海岸小镇与寺庙遗址，一直到城市中心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名受过严格火器与格斗训练的特种兵，你必须运用射击、刺杀、踢击、反击等多种专业能力自我防卫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/5b8e92141a88bf26fc42cec753747147.poster.avif?t=1762784991\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/5b8e92141a88bf26fc42cec753747147.webm?t=1762784991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/5b8e92141a88bf26fc42cec753747147.mp4?t=1762784991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精进战斗技巧，获得奖励。击杀越精准高效，获得的“基因点数”越多。这些点数可用于兑换强大的装备升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎战巨大而恐怖的 Boss 敌人。徐妍完全没料到，城市中心的异变会如此失控。必须做好万全准备，任何事都可能发生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/4ebae81b62b4568310c3bb6107b7f976.poster.avif?t=1762784991\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/4ebae81b62b4568310c3bb6107b7f976.webm?t=1762784991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340130/extras/4ebae81b62b4568310c3bb6107b7f976.mp4?t=1762784991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重温经典生存恐怖游戏的魅力。通过固定视角与预渲染背景，融合解谜机制、自定义难度与可选的坦克式操作，唤起玩家对复古恐怖作品的熟悉记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁丰富的额外内容：替换服装、附加模式与隐藏结局，等待那些足够好奇、敢于深入探索的玩家去发现。</p></li></ul>",
